quran[23]{c,v,t}:
  27,82,N’imvugo mugihe izoba shikira tuzoba kurira igikoko ngaha kw’Isi kizoba vugisha abo bantu kubera yuko batemera amajambo yacu
  27,83,"N’umusi tuzo kwegeranya mumirwi y’abantu bahakanye Imana yabo y’ukuri, nabone bazoshigwa mumirwi nk’abandi"
  27,84,"N’igihe bazoshika Imana izovumera iti:- mbega mwebwe mwarahakanye amajambo yanje mutabizi neza, canke mwamye mugira iki"
  27,85,"Ijambo ry’ukuri rizobashikira kubera yuko bahemutse, rero ntaco bazovuga"
  27,86,"Mbega ntibabona yuko twaremye Ijoro kugira ngo abantu baruhukire mwo hamwe n’umutaga w’umuco, mu vy’ukuri muri ibi vyose harimwo ibimenyetso kubantu bemera Imana yabo y’ukuri"
  27,87,"N’umusi hazovuzwa inzamba hanyuma abari mumajuru nabari kw’isi bose baze bate imitwe hirya no hino, dukuyemwo uwo Imana yashakiye ntate umutwe wiwe hirya no hino, na bose bazoyi shikira nabo bafise ibimaramare"
  27,88,"Uzobona imisozi ukibaza yuko ihumuye nayo iriko iragenda nk’ibicu, uko niko Imana ikora kuko yakoze ibintu vyose, ntankeka niyo ifise inkuru y’ivyo mugira vyose"
  27,89,"Abazozana ineza bazoronka ineza gusumba iyo, nuko kuburagizwa kw’uwo musi bazoba bari mumahoro nawo"
  27,90,"Nabazogira ububisha bwabo amaso yabo azotabwa mumuriro udahera, none ntimuhembwa atari kuvyo mwahora mugira"
  27,91,"Ntankeka nategetswe ngo nsenge Umuremyi w’iki gisagara, ariwe yagiteye iteka kandi ibintu vyose nivyiwe kandi nkaba nategetswe yuko noba mubantu babagamburutsi"
  27,92,"Kandi nsome iyi Qur’aani ntagatifu, nukuba ndi mubarongotse, nuwurongotse aba arongotse kubwiwe, nayo uwazimiye wewe nuvuge uti:- mu vy’ukuri jewe ndi mu bantu batuza abantu"
  27,93,"Kandi uvuge iti:- ihayagizwa ryose ryiza ni ry’Imana kuko ubu vuba Imana izobereka ibimenyetso vyayo kandi muzobitahura, kandi umuremyi wawe ntiyibagira kuri ibi vyose mugira"
  28,1,"Twa, Siiyn, Miiym, (Insiguro y’izi ndome hamwe nuwufise ubumenyi bwazo bwose n’Imana yonyene gusa)"
  28,2,Aya n’amajambo y’Imana matagatifu ari mugitabu kiri k’umugaragaro
  28,3,Tugusomera inkuru y’intumwa y’Imana Mussa (iii) hamwe n’inkuru ya Fir’aauni bimwe vy’ukuri kubera abantu bemera bimwe bivuye k’umutima
  28,4,"Mu vy’ukuri Fir’aauni yarigize akagarama ruganda kuri iy’Isi, hanyuma agira abantu bayo imirwi itandukanye n’iyindi, atako acinyiza umurwi umwe muribo mugukerera ibibondo vyabo vy’abahungu nugusiga ibibondo vy’abigeme bikirizi bizima, mu vy’ukuri uyo Fir’auni yari mu bantu b’abononyi"
  28,5,Hanyuma twashatse kubagirira impuhwe bamwe bacinyizwa kuri iyo Si nukubagira abategetsi nukubagira basamurarwa wayo mahirwe
  28,6,Nukubaha ingoga ngaha kw’Isi mukwereka Fir’auni hamwe na Hamana n’ingabo zabo kuvyo bahora batinya
  28,7,"Twaramweretse nyina w’intumwa y’Imana Mussa (iii) yuko yokwonsa ikibondo ciwe no mugihe yoba amufitiye amakenga nace umushira mumwonga kandi ntatinye canke ngo agire agahinda, kuko twebwe tuzomugarura iwawe kandi tuzomugira mubazoba bari intumwa z’Imana"
  28,8,"Rero abantu bokwa Fir’auni nibo bamutoye kugira ngo abe umwansi hagati yabo n’agahinda, ntankeka Fir’auni na Hamana hamwe n’ingabo zabo bari mu bantu babi cane"
  28,9,"N’umukenyezi wa Fir’auni yavuze abwira Fir’auni ati:- ntumwice uyu azoba uwuzo nezereza amaso kuri jewe nawewe, kandi ntimumwice nkumbure azotugirira akandi kamaro, canke tumwitirire yuko ari ikibondo cacu mugihe nabo batabizi"
  28,10,N’umutima w’umuvyeyikazi w’intumwa y’Imana Mussa (iii) usigara atakirimwo kuko yari hafi yugu serura amabanga iyo tudahumuriza umutima wiwe kugira ngo abe mubemera Imana yiwe y’ukuri
  28,11,"Abwira mushikiwe ati:- n’umukurikire, nawe aramwitegereza ari kure yabo nabo batabizi"